  25 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> haddock-0.4.ebuild,
  haddock-0.5.ebuild, haddock-0.6-r1.ebuild, haddock-0.6-r2.ebuild,
  haddock-0.6.ebuild:
